# noise-record

Monorepo for the **NoiseRecord** iOS app and its product website.

## Projects

| Path | Description |
|------|-------------|
| [`NoiseRecord/`](NoiseRecord/) | SwiftUI iOS app — noise monitoring, voice-activated recording, video evidence |
| [`website/`](website/) | Static product landing site (HTML/CSS/JS) |

The website folder is **not** part of the Xcode target. Changes to `website/` do not affect the iOS build.

## Website

- **Local preview:** `cd website && python3 -m http.server 8080`
- **Deploy:** Push to `main` — GitHub Actions deploys to GitHub Pages (see [`website/README.md`](website/README.md))
- **Custom domain:** `noise.nx.kg` — DNS & GitHub Pages steps in [`website/README.md`](website/README.md)

## iOS app

Open `NoiseRecord/NoiseRecord.xcodeproj` in Xcode. Requires iOS 18.6+.

